name: Nature's True Fruit
desc: This fruit, brought as a memento from Sumeru by the Teapot Traveling Salesman Chubby, gives off a truly marvelous fragrance. Even a whiff of this fruit brings certain images to mind, which you can manipulate via the power of Sub-Space Creation to recreate the wondrous sights of Sumeru in your Realm Within...

value.text: Used to unlock the realm 'Sublime Spicewood' in the Serenitea Pot.
Tubby's Realm Depot in the Serenitea Pot
